entries.journal_entry_description: Report to Wilson Tchorshel in Kadaara and give him the droid modules.
entries.journal_entry_title: Bring the Droid Modules to Wilson Tchorshel
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Standby for an incoming transmission from Wilson Tchorshel.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Well done! You've collected the droid modules, and more importantly, kept them out of the corrupt hands of the Empire. Bring them to me in Kadaara.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Well done! You've collected the droid modules, and more importantly, kept them out of the corrupt hands of the Empire. Bring them to me in Kadaara.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Go to Kadaara and speak with Wilson Tchorshel. He eagerly awaits you and the droid modules you've collected.
